      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_announcements" data-step-uuid="3AF20963-4014-4F12-9279-065FE6C07EF4">
    <h2 id="open_announcements" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcements</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/744/183/original/e750ab35-85bb-47a7-965c-e6b1a69efe8e.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcements" height="312" width="173">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_99083C60-22EA-0135-315A-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p><a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-view-my-Canvas-groups-as-a-student/ta-p/281" target="_blank">Open a group</a> in which you are a member.<span style="color:rgb(38,38,38);"> Then, in Group Navigation, click the <strong>Announcements</strong> link.</span></p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="add_announcement_in_group_home_page" data-step-uuid="EA71AD3D-1F7C-42AD-AD6A-87C15639DBF1">
    <h3 id="add_announcement_in_group_home_page" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Add Announcement in Group Home Page</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/700/original/38853552-6ef1-4b19-8171-69d45ba01208.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/700/medium/38853552-6ef1-4b19-8171-69d45ba01208.png" srcset="" alt="Add Announcement in Group Home Page" height="346" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_990874B0-22EA-0135-315C-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>You can also add an announcement in a group by clicking the Group Navigation <strong>Home</strong> link [1] and then clicking the <strong>Add Announcement</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
