      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_9908D360-22EA-0135-315E-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Add Announcement</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="add_content" data-step-uuid="77BE357F-05D2-4C9C-8126-87CD4A8C783E">
    <h2 id="add_content" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Create Announcement</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/704/original/533a37d6-22bd-44f7-af85-0ae2c64b3f40.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/704/medium/533a37d6-22bd-44f7-af85-0ae2c64b3f40.png" srcset="" alt="Create Announcement" height="675" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_99090650-22EA-0135-3160-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Enter an announcement title in the <strong>Topic Title</strong> field [1].</p>
<p>Add content using the <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-menubar-in-the-Rich-Content-Editor-as-a-student/ta-p/357" target="_blank">Rich Content Editor</a> [2]. A word count displays [3].</p>
<p>If enabled by your instructor, you can allow other users to like the announcement. To allow other users to like the announcement, click the <strong>Allow liking</strong> checkbox [4].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="save_announcement" data-step-uuid="28CB3802-31E0-4DFE-A5E8-7AEBF675D834">
    <h2 id="save_announcement" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Publish Announcement</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/707/original/def64874-9b74-466d-9727-df6d2d26922d.png" srcset="" alt="Publish Announcement" height="75" width="188">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_99093950-22EA-0135-3162-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Publish</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_announcement" data-step-uuid="2C5A7121-289A-476E-A2F4-A6931736B0F8">
    <h2 id="view_announcement" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Announcement</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/709/original/8696a06f-6e20-46be-b233-a83c2b4739db.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/536/709/medium/8696a06f-6e20-46be-b233-a83c2b4739db.png" srcset="" alt="View Announcement" height="428" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_393c6f21-55a7-4032-a05d-b5f4520607b9" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View the announcement. </p>
<p>To manage the announcement, click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [1], then select an option [2]. You can mark the announcement as read, mark the announcement as unread, <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-edit-an-announcement-in-a-group/ta-p/459" target="_blank">edit the announcement</a>, or <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-delete-an-announcement-in-a-group/ta-p/457" target="_blank">delete it</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

